description: Ireland's deputy PM says passing a confidential medical deal to a friend was "not best practice".
title: Leo Varadkar apologises for 'errors of judgement' after document leak
title_page: Leo Varadkar apologises for 'errors of judgement' after document leak - BBC News
maintext: He conceded that what he had done was "not best practice" but he had couriered the document to his friend to get wider backing from doctors for the new contract.
